FileCore_MiscOp 7 (3.60+)
#Parent FileCore_MiscOp
=>	R0 =	7 (reason code)
	R1 =	drive number
	R8 =	pointer to FileCore instance private word

<=	R2 =	flags	b0 set: drive locked
 	 	 	b1 set: drive hidden from the iconbar

This call read flags about the drive.
#line;tab
See <PRM 5a-175=>PRM-5a:175>.
